How to style JORTS? ⬇️

🔖Balance the proportions- wear with a fitted or cropped tee since they are long and loose.

•Keeps the shape visible
Think fitted tops, bodysuits or bralettes 

Long tops that hang over jorts can make you look off or shorten your legs

🔖High-rise mid-length jorts elongate the legs and define the waist

🔖Keep the footwear or socks till ankles to give a balance proportion
